high_descs: turn to the left and go to the wall and turn to the left and go to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and take out the tomato from the refrigerator and close the refrigerator door
turn to the left and take a few steps and turn to the right facing the sink
put the tomato in the sink and turn on the water to fill the sink and turn off and drain the water and pick up the tomato from the sink
turn to the right and take a step and turn to the left and step to the waste basket
put the tomato in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed tomato in the waste basket

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall, then hang a left and walk up to the fridge.
Open the fridge and take the tomato out of the fridge, then close the fridge door.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then turn right to face the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink then pick it back up.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left to face the small grey bin in between the counter and fridge.
Put the clean tomato in the grey bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean tomato in a grey bin.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the fridge.
Take the tomato from the fridge.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Wash the tomato in the sink. Take the tomato from the sink.
Go to the right of the sink to the trash bin.
Put the tomato in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed tomato in a trash bin.
